             <p>Welcome to PATHLAB Diagnostics, the online portal of Lupin Healthcare Limited (“<strong>Lupin Healthcare</strong>”). The domain name <a href="http://www.lupindiagnostics.com">www.lupindiagnostics.com</a> (“<strong>Platform</strong>”) is owned and managed by Lupin Healthcare. Lupin Healthcare intends to provide to the User a Platform consisting of various health care packages and other health related Services at affordable rates (“<strong>Services</strong>”). Lupin Healthcare is a public limited company, incorporated and existing under the laws of India having our registered office at 3rd Floor, Kalpataru Inspire, Off Western Express Highway, Santacruz (East), Mumbai - 400055.</p>
