            <p><strong>1. Nature and Applicability</strong></p>
            <p>The Terms and Conditions which set out legally binding obligations and conditions of use of the Platform and Services (“<strong>Terms</strong>”) shall apply to all Users who are interested in accessing the Platform and availing the Services contained on the Platform. Users shall mean customers, persons, entities or anyone who visits, deals with, transacts and uses or is interested in availing one or more Services provided through the Platform (“<strong>Users</strong>”).</p>
            <p>User is requested to carefully go through the Terms as well as the <a href="@Url.Action("Cookie", "Info")">Cookie Policy</a> and <a href="@Url.Action("Privacy", "Info")">Privacy Policy</a> before availing the Services. By accessing the Platform, User represents and confirms that User has read and understood and is bound by the Terms as well as the Privacy Policy.</p>
            <p>The Terms are subject to change at any time at the discretion of Lupin Healthcare and it is User’s responsibility to check the Terms prior to booking any Services.</p>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <p><strong>2. Copyright Policy and Ownership</strong></p>
