            <p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
            <p><strong>3. Eligibility</strong></p>
            <p>By using/ accessing the Platform, User represents and confirms that User has the right, authority and capacity to abide by these Terms, Cookie Policy and Privacy Policy. User further confirms that User is a citizen of India and if required will provide necessary documentation such as Aadhaar card etc. to establish the same.</p>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <p><strong>4. Description of Services</strong></p>
            <p>The User will be entitled to the following Services:</p>
            <ol>
            <li>Access the Platform and view Health Packages and list of individual tests. User will be able to book Services, use chatbot and payment gateway, which are integral part of the Platform.</li>
            <li>Book one or more Service upon providing the requested details such as name, address, mobile number and other information along with medical prescription of the doctor (if required and applicable). User is required to carry requisite documents as may be required for availing the Service. Lupin Healthcare may also provide home collection service, subject to availability.</li>
            <li>The test report shall be provided to the User by way of a weblink which will be shared on the phone number of the user, provided at the time of booking the Service. User will be able to download the test report and shall be able to save the same in his/ her mobile phone or tab for future access. The Platform shall store the test reports of the User for a period of two (2) years, post which the same shall be deleted from the Platform. If required, User can also collect the test reports from any of the PATHLAB Diagnostics centers.</li>
            <li>In case User is facing any issue with booking or requires any clarification with respect to any of the Services, User shall be able to receive requisite assistance or support to resolve such queries.</li>
            <li>In case of deficiency or non-performance of Services by any our Associates, User shall be required to notify the same to Lupin Healthcare, within a period of two (2) working days, by calling at 7030 300 400 or writing to <a href="mailto:customerconnect@lupindiagnostics.com">customerconnect@lupindiagnostics.com</a>. Lupin Healthcare shall take appropriate steps to provide adequate remedy after verifying the claim.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
