            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <p><strong>6. Booking and payment for Services</strong></p>
            <p>User can avail the Services by booking a home collection or by visiting the nearest lab as provided on the Platform. The Platform will guide the User with a step-by-step process to book the Service based on the mobile number provided by the User. In case the User is already registered or has earlier booked Services through the Platform, the existing details of the User will be verified by way of a One Time Password (OTP) so that the User is not required to enter the details once again while booking.</p>
            <p>Once the User has availed a Service, a receipt will be generated which will also enable the User to download the test report once the same is issued by the respective lab. The Platform shall store the test reports of the User for a period of two (2) years, post which the same shall be deleted from the Platform. The User can also collect the test reports from any of the PATHLAB Diagnostics centers.</p>
            <p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
            <p><strong>7. Payment</strong></p>
            <p>All prices will be charged in GBP and shall be inclusive of taxes. User will be able to avail the Services upon making full payment either in cash or through online payment method. In case User intends to make payment online, User will be redirected to third party payment gateways. For home collection, an additional fee will be charged. In case User intends to receive refund of an amount which has been inadvertently paid to the Platform or has been paid in excess, then the User can send an email to <a href="mailto:customerconnect@lupindiagnostics.com">customerconnect@lupindiagnostics.com</a>, claiming a refund. The refund will be issued to the User within 10- 12 working days after verifying the claim. &nbsp;</p>
