            <p>Use of the Platform shall be governed by Lupin Healthcare’s Privacy Policy. Lupin Healthcare shall endeavor to keep all information disclosed by the Users confidential at all times and use the same only for the purpose for which the information has been disclosed. However, Lupin Healthcare shall not be liable to User, directly or indirectly, for disclosure of any information which is not asked/called upon for the purpose of performing the booked Services. &nbsp;</p>
